I"h<p>This feature allows you to change your displayed name, your email, add a description about yourself, add your account to the website’s subscribers and change your password. You can also upload a profile picture!</p>

<p><strong>How to edit your profile?</strong></p>

<p>Visit the website, log in and choose <strong>Edit Profile</strong> on the dropdown menu on the right of the header, as you can see in the example below.</p>

